OL,3,CFlooding causes rail disruption
OL,4,Cbetween Cardiff and Treherbert
OL,6,FTrain services are disrupted between
OL,7,FCardiff and Treherbert and flooding on
OL,8,Fthe line around Pontypridd.
OL,10,FAs a result Transport for Wales said
OL,11,Fit would be running a reduced hourly
OL,12,Fservice will run between Tonypandy and
OL,13,FTreherbert only.
OL,15,FTrains will not run between Treherbert
OL,16,Fand Cardiff Central on the full route
OL,17,Fwith disruptions expected to continue
OL,18,Funtil Monday afternoon
