OL,3,CFlooding causes rail disruption
OL,4,Cbetween Cardiff and Treherbert
OL,6,FRail replacement transport is running
OL,7,Fbetween Radyr and Treherbert until the
OL,8,Fline fully reopens.
OL,10,FIt's expected sunshine and scattered
OL,11,Fshowers will follow weather warnings
OL,12,Fissued over the weekend for heavy rain
OL,13,Fand deep floodwater.
OL,15,FThe Met Office issued an amber weather
OL,16,Fwarning for heavy rain and deep
OL,17,Ffloodwater that could cause "danger to
OL,18,Flife", as it said flooding and
OL,19,Fdisruption was likely "overnight into
OL,20,FMonday".
