OL,3,CFlooding causes rail disruption
OL,4,Cbetween Cardiff and Treherbert
OL,6,FThe warning covered south and mid-
OL,7,FWales, from Newport to Carmarthen and
OL,8,Fnorth to Brecon, between 3pm on Sunday
OL,9,Fand 6am on Monday.
OL,11,FYellow weather warnings for rain also
OL,12,Fcame into force for south-west England
OL,13,Fand much of the rest of south and mid-
OL,14,FWales from midday on Sunday until 8am
OL,15,Fon Monday.
OL,17,FNatural Resources Wales has seven
OL,18,Fflood warnings in place as of 6am,
OL,19,Falong with 30 flood alerts.
