OL,3,CFlooding causes rail disruption
OL,4,Cbetween Cardiff and Treherbert
OL,6,FAndrew Morgan, leader of Rhondda Cynon
OL,7,FTaf council, said Sunday had been a
OL,8,F"close call" after thousands of
OL,9,Fsandbags were distributed to high-risk
OL,10,Fareas.
OL,12,FHundreds of homes and businesses in
OL,13,Fthe area were flooded in November by
OL,14,FStorm Bert.
OL,16,FMr Morgan told PA on Sunday night:
OL,17,F"It's been a busy day for the dozens
OL,18,Fof crews and contractors on stand-by.
