OL,4,Cbetween Cardiff and Treherbert
OL,6,F"Overall, while there has been
OL,7,Fisolated issues with culverts, the
OL,8,Fmajority of calls has been for surface
OL,9,Fwater flooding and highways.
OL,11,F"Today has, I believe, been a close
OL,12,Fcall from rivers flooding in some
OL,13,Fareas. I will be discussing this with
OL,14,FNatural Resources Wales in the coming
OL,15,Fdays."
